# Locked hero objects (5)

Read `docs/KWALIFY_VISUAL_STYLE_DNA.md` and `docs/KWALIFY_HERO_OBJECTS_LOCKED.md` before any hero, scene, or mood card work.

Allowed heroes only: `pump` `road` `lamp` `car` `horizon`

Each emotion screen:
- ONE hero object (sharpest layer)
- L1 abstract gradient only
- L2 minimal ambient (optional)
- NO environments, buildings, cars in scene (except car hero itself), canopy, sky, horizon lines unless hero IS horizon strip

Figma: `docs/KWALIFY_FIGMA_EMOTION_SCENE_UI.md`

FAILSAFE: If output is blobs, fog, or multi-focal scenery → STOP. Replace with geometric hero from locked spec.

Do not add new hero types without updating the locked doc and WORLD_MOODS in index.html.
